data.description: Welcome to a spacious 2-story home that's surely an absolutely beautiful home in North Merced in the Silverado Estates. Situated on a large corner lot in a cul-de-sac, this beautifully home offers an open floor plan for all your perfect entertainments! This home provides plenty of space for every inside and outside gathering. Home includes 4 bedrooms 2.5 bath with many features that makes it the perfect family home. There is a bonus room that can be used as an office or potentially an extra bedroom. You'll love this awesome kitchen that includes a kitchen island and lots of cabinet space for all the kitchenware. Relax in the family room overseeing the beautiful in ground pool. This home has plenty of windows to light up this beauty with the perfect sun light. The amazing backyard with the in ground pool for them summer days to spend entertaining friends and family. Master bedroom has a bay window, walking closet, and separate shower and tub. Home sits in a well establish neighborhood and location is key! You're minutes away from the park, Sprouts or Raley's plaza, Merced College and UC Merced.
